@startuml
start
:User navigates to Home Screen;
:Request latest vehicle status data;
fork
  'Battery and Range Processing
  :Fetch State of Charge (SoC), consumption trends, and ambient temperature;
  :Calculate estimated vehicle range;
  if (User's preferred unit is Kilometers?) then (yes)
    :Format range in KM;
  else (no)
    :Format range in Miles;
  endif
  :Format SoC as percentage value;
  :Generate visual representation of battery level from SoC;

fork again
  'Security and Climate Processing
  :Fetch vehicle lock status;
  :Fetch interior cabin temperature;
  :Fetch climate control activity status;

fork again
  'Visual Asset Processing
  :Load graphical representation of user's vehicle;

fork end
:Assemble all data components for display;
:Render Home Screen with all vehicle information;
stop
@enduml